# TsunDal - A Tsun Bossfight Overhaul
- Author: ENR
- Game: skyrimspecialedition
- Mod Page: https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrimspecialedition/mods/59661


![](data:image/png;base64,)
  
  
Overhauls the Tsun bossfight, giving him more health and magic attacks to help make him more challenging.
  
  
He is extremely tanky and aggressive. Occasionally, he will summon his companion, Maithan to support him.
  
  
![](https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/1704/images/59661/59661-1638862006-417647814.png)﻿
  
Once you defeat him, him and his bear will be available as **summons**.
  
Pass into the Hall of Valor, look to your left and you will find a shrine with all of his items and three spells inside a strongbox.
  
The armor is male only but the horns are unisex.
  
  
![](https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/1704/images/59661/59661-1638862020-323628705.png)﻿
  
Mathain can be ridden as a Mount.
  
  
![](https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/1704/images/59661/59661-1638862037-1770548756.png)﻿
